# Advanced Filtering API Examples

## Attribute Filtering

### Basic attribute search with pagination
GET /attributes?search=color&page=1&limit=10

### Filter by user-friendly type
GET /attributes?userFriendlyType=text&sortBy=name&sortOrder=asc

### Filter by date (latest/newest first)
GET /attributes?dateFilter=latest&limit=20

### Filter attributes with default values
GET /attributes?hasDefaultValue=true&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc

### Filter attributes that are in groups
GET /attributes?inGroups=true&search=size

### Complex attribute filtering
GET /attributes?search=product&userFriendlyType=number&hasDefaultValue=true&sortBy=updatedAt&sortOrder=desc&page=1&limit=15

### Filter by date range
GET /attributes?createdAfter=2024-01-01&createdBefore=2024-12-31&sortBy=name

## Attribute Groups Filtering

### Search attribute groups by name or description
GET /attributes/groups?search=product&sortBy=totalAttributes&sortOrder=desc

### Filter groups with descriptions
GET /attributes/groups?hasDescription=true&sortBy=name&sortOrder=asc

### Filter by attribute count range
GET /attributes/groups?minAttributes=3&maxAttributes=10&dateFilter=latest

### Complex group filtering
GET /attributes/groups?search=product&hasDescription=true&minAttributes=2&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc

## Family Filtering

### Basic family search
GET /families?search=electronics&page=1&limit=10

### Sort by total products
GET /families?sortBy=totalProducts&sortOrder=desc

### Sort by total attributes
GET /families?sortBy=totalAttributes&sortOrder=asc

### Filter by families containing specific attributes (ANY of the attributes)
GET /families?attributeIds=1,2,3&attributeFilter=any&sortBy=name

### Filter by families containing ALL specified attributes
GET /families?attributeIds=1,2&attributeFilter=all&sortBy=totalProducts&sortOrder=desc

### Filter families with products
GET /families?hasProducts=true&sortBy=totalProducts&sortOrder=desc

### Filter families with required attributes
GET /families?hasRequiredAttributes=true&sortBy=name&sortOrder=asc

### Filter by product count range
GET /families?minProducts=5&maxProducts=50&sortBy=totalProducts&sortOrder=desc

### Filter by attribute count range
GET /families?minAttributes=3&maxAttributes=15&sortBy=totalAttributes&sortOrder=desc

### Complex family filtering
GET /families?search=phone&attributeIds=1,2&attributeFilter=any&hasProducts=true&minProducts=10&sortBy=totalProducts&sortOrder=desc&page=1&limit=20

### Filter by date range
GET /families?createdAfter=2024-01-01&dateFilter=latest&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc

## Advanced Use Cases

### Find recent attributes of specific types
GET /attributes?userFriendlyType=number&dateFilter=latest&limit=5

### Find families with many products but few attributes
GET /families?minProducts=20&maxAttributes=5&sortBy=totalProducts&sortOrder=desc

### Find attribute groups with specific characteristics
GET /attributes/groups?hasDescription=true&minAttributes=5&sortBy=totalAttributes&sortOrder=desc

### Search with multiple criteria
GET /families?search=mobile&hasProducts=true&hasRequiredAttributes=true&sortBy=name&sortOrder=asc

## Response Format

All filtered endpoints return paginated responses with the following structure:

```json
{
  "data": [...], // Array of items
  "pagination": {
    "page": 1,
    "limit": 10,
    "total": 100,
    "totalPages": 10,
    "hasNext": true,
    "hasPrev": false
  }
}
```

## Available Sort Fields

### Attributes
- `name` (default)
- `type` 
- `createdAt`
- `updatedAt`
- `totalAttributes` (for groups)

### Families
- `name` (default)
- `createdAt`
- `updatedAt`
- `totalProducts`
- `totalAttributes`

## Available Sort Orders
- `asc` (ascending, default)
- `desc` (descending)

## Date Filters
- `latest` - Sort by most recent first
- `oldest` - Sort by oldest first
